{"tid":1516539,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[緊急]請立即停止以「白色恐怖」一詞描述香港慘況","createTime":"2019-08-29T15:04:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T14:16:49.000Z","uid":248120,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0ac941317141063636e6dcd1bb8f450f6bbf9c25","tid":1516539,"uid":248120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:04:17.000Z","msg":"<strong>依家開始<br />\n請將近來中共及各界對香港基本權既恐慌性打壓稱作</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">紅　色　恐　怖</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong>唔好再用「白色恐怖」伊個字！</strong><br />\n<br />\n因爲中共係第二世界國家，屬共產陣營<br />\n計正應該以「<span style=\"color: red;\">紅色</span>」來象徵同共產黨有關既事物<br />\n<br />\n而「白色恐怖」伊個字<br />\n係愛來描述<strong>保守主義、資本主義</strong>陣營所引起既恐慌性壓迫<br />\n例如：麥卡錫、蔣中正、朴正熙等政權<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但香港依家個terror唔係乜野白色恐怖啊！<br />\n係「<span style=\"color: red;\">紅色恐怖</span>」先啱啊！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n香港發生緊既<br />\n係共產黨有份資助、發動、鼓勵既恐怖行爲<br />\n而唔係各在野黨、保守黨、甚至香城online玩家發動架！<br />\n<br />\n唔好以爲個個令言論、人才、政敵消失既<br />\n都叫做「白恐」至係架！<br />\n橫掂你一路都講開乜乜乜俾人「<span style=\"color: red;\">染紅</span>」、而唔係被人「染白」啊嘛！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n註：紅色恐怖亦可稱作「赤色恐怖」"},{"pid":"f3965a04053563de1da5ec868aa7ea35b7852a65","tid":1516539,"uid":248120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:15:16.000Z","msg":"0342<br />\n1788<br />\n7449<br />\n3263<br />\n2514<br />\n0108<br />\n7245<br />\n0730"},{"pid":"c61400ce4a350c0f03ce89af4b4d89036ad1ba11","tid":1516539,"uid":98926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T15:19:48.000Z","msg":"定「血色恐怖」？<br />\n<br />\n831遊行<br />\n831<span style=\"color: red;\">死線</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/npq7Ds0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnpq7Ds0.jpg&h=cd008a46&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d910d8648dfda65d7bf0df789f79bc913b631884","tid":1516539,"uid":308567,"li